            "--- ‚úÇÔ∏è Data Split Statistics ---\n",
            "Training Set:   45820 rows\n",
            "Test Set:       5728 rows\n",
            "Manual Set:     5728 rows\n",
            "\n",
            "--- üíæ Creating Validation File ---\n",
            "‚úÖ SUCCESS: 'Manual_Validation_Set.csv' has been created.\n",
            "   (Open this file to pick Lat/Lon/State for testing)\n",
            "\n",
            "üöÄ Training Model on Remaining 80% Data...\n"
          ]
